MERCHANTABILITY or FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE.

Prerequisites
-------------
The following extra modules that can be downloaded from CPAN are required for
some functions:
Image::Magick

Installation
------------

perl Makefile.PL
make
make install
perldoc SMS::Image

Author
------

Craig Manley c.manley@skybound.nl